    description: "Section: Career Distribution • Framing: his article illuminates how key milestones—from the excitement of marriage and welcoming a new baby to navigating pivotal career changes and planning for retirement—all present crucial opportunities to integrate both health coverage and wealth planning. It provides a roadmap for agents to view each client not just through a single transaction but across the entire continuum of their evolving needs. • Goal: The goal of this article is to empower AmeriLife Career Distribution agents to elevate their client relationships from transactional to truly consultative. By embracing a \"whole-person approach,\" agents will gain the insights and strategies needed to proactively address clients' evolving needs in health and wealth planning as they move through different life stages. This will enable agents to provide more holistic, enduring value, deepen client loyalty, and uncover opportunities for comprehensive planning that supports financial stability and well-being at every turn.",
